class.name: ExecuTorchMV2Demo
class.brief_description: Demo node for ExecuTorch MobileNet v2 inference integration in Godot.
class.description: This node provides a minimal demonstration of running ExecuTorch MobileNet v2 model inference within Godot. It loads a .pte model file and performs inference with dummy input data, printing results to the console. [b]Note:[/b] This is a basic demo implementation. For production use, additional error handling and optimization would be needed.

method.name: _ready
method.description: Called when the node is added to the scene. Loads the model and performs demo inference if model_path is set.

members.member: Path to the .pte model file to load for inference.
